  "title": "Fitting a non-linear model with errors in both variables and its application",
  "abstract": "Estimation of the parameters of a non-linear model is considered when both measured variables have random errors. The maximum likelihood estimates with the asymptotic variance and covariance matrix are presented. Real data are used to illustrate the procedure discussed",
